description:
In this week's mini-episode, Kate and Doree get right to questions. They talk about the conversations that should happen before you move in with a partner, their favorite forms of congratulatory self-care, and how to take care of yourself when you don't have extra money to spend.

To learn more, visit www.forever35podcast.com.

Theme music by Riot.
